news.title: Where EV Stocks Are Going In 2025
news.content: The electric vehicle market lost some juice earlier in 2024, but October showed a sector comeback with some serious battery power. According to Cox Automotive, new EV sales were up 2.3% for the month and have cleared one million units for the year to date.

news.title: Even in 2023, Charlie Munger Said 'Elon Musk Overestimates Himself' But Credited His Success to One Key Factor
news.content: At Berkshire Hathaway's 2023 annual meeting, Charlie Munger-Warren Buffett's longtime business partner - once again shared his thoughts on Elon Musk, the billionaire CEO behind Tesla, SpaceX and Starlink. When asked if he still believes Musk "overestimates himself, " Munger didn't hold back."
